platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: A fun way to learn a language

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With its friendly approach and awesome updates, Duolingos long been one of our favorite apps for learning another language. Its secret: making the process genuinely fun. Engaging mini-games test your reading, writing, and speaking skills, and joining a club (where you can encourage and compete with others) adds a great social element. Bonus: all those languages and games are available for free!
One of our favourite apps for learning another language, the process is genuinely fun. Whats more, all those languages and games are available for free!
